# INNTEK AI API AGENT — Universal Software Blueprint
# Version: 3.0.0 | Last Sync: 2026-03-03

## 1. Overview

**Project:** AI Agent Integrations Platform — a full-stack web application for creating, managing, and executing AI-powered tools with multi-provider support and a visual workflow orchestrator (Machines).

**Business Purpose:** Enable non-technical users to build AI processing pipelines through a drag-and-drop interface, chain tools into automated flows, and execute them against multiple AI providers with structured JSON output validation.

