## 6. Database Schema

### 6.1 Roles
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK, auto-generated |
| nombre | STRING | unique, not null |

### 6.2 Privilegios
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| ref_modulo | STRING | not null (`*` for wildcard) |
| read | BOOLEAN | default: false |
| write | BOOLEAN | default: false |
| exec | BOOLEAN | default: false |
| role_id | UUID | FK → Roles.id |

### 6.3 Users
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | not null |
| email | STRING | unique, not null |
| password | STRING | not null (bcrypt) |
| role_id | UUID | FK → Roles.id |

### 6.4 Tools
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | not null |
| descripcion | TEXT | — |
| logo_herramienta | STRING | emoji |
| training_prompt | TEXT | System Instruction: Context |
| behavior_prompt | TEXT | System Instruction: Behavior |
| response_format | STRING | JSON / Text / Markdown |
| output_format_id | UUID | FK → OutputFormats.id (nullable) |
| json_schema_id | UUID | FK → JsonSchemas.id (nullable) |
| ai_provider_id | UUID | FK → AiProviders.id (nullable, override) |

### 6.5 JsonSchemas
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | not null |
| descripcion | TEXT | — |
| schema | TEXT | not null (JSON Schema string) |

### 6.6 OutputCategories
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | unique, not null |

### 6.7 OutputFormats
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | not null |
| tipo | ENUM | reporte, accionable, generativo |
| estructura | TEXT | not null (HTML template with `{{placeholder}}`) |
| category_id | UUID | FK → OutputCategories.id |

### 6.8 Configs
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| key | STRING | unique, not null |
| value | TEXT | — |

### 6.9 AiProviders
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | not null |
| slug | STRING | unique, not null |
| tipo | ENUM | google_native, openai_compatible |
| api_key | STRING | — (masked on read) |
| base_url | STRING | — (null for google_native) |
| modelo | STRING | not null |
| is_default | BOOLEAN | default: false |
| activo | BOOLEAN | default: true |
| extra_headers | TEXT | JSON string for custom HTTP headers |

### 6.10 Engines
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | not null |
| slug | STRING | unique, not null |
| descripcion | TEXT | — |
| tipo | ENUM | iterator, collector, mapper |
| icono | STRING | emoji |
| config_schema | TEXT | JSON string |
| activo | BOOLEAN | default: true |

### 6.11 Machines
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| nombre | STRING | not null |
| descripcion | TEXT | — |
| icono | STRING | emoji |
| activo | BOOLEAN | default: true |

### 6.12 MachineNodes
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| machine_id | UUID | FK → Machines.id (CASCADE) |
| node_type | ENUM | tool, engine |
| tool_id | UUID | FK → Tools.id (nullable) |
| engine_id | UUID | FK → Engines.id (nullable) |
| position_x | FLOAT | default: 0 |
| position_y | FLOAT | default: 0 |
| config | TEXT | JSON string |

### 6.13 MachineConnections
| Column | Type | Constraints |
|--------|------|-------------|
| id | UUID | PK |
| machine_id | UUID | FK → Machines.id (CASCADE) |
| source_node_id | UUID | FK → MachineNodes.id |
| target_node_id | UUID | FK → MachineNodes.id |
| source_handle | STRING | — |
| target_handle | STRING | — |

### Associations
```
Role 1──N Privilegio (role_id)
Role 1──N User (role_id)
OutputCategory 1──N OutputFormat (category_id)
OutputFormat 1──N Tool (output_format_id)
JsonSchema 1──N Tool (json_schema_id)
AiProvider 1──N Tool (ai_provider_id)
Machine 1──N MachineNode (machine_id, CASCADE)
Machine 1──N MachineConnection (machine_id, CASCADE)
MachineNode N──1 Tool (tool_id)
MachineNode N──1 Engine (engine_id)
MachineConnection N──1 MachineNode as SourceNode (source_node_id)
MachineConnection N──1 MachineNode as TargetNode (target_node_id)
```

