## 7. API Endpoints

All routes prefixed with `/api`. Protected by `authMiddleware` + `requirePrivilege`.

### Auth (Public)
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| POST | `/auth/login` | Login, returns JWT + user + privileges | Public |
| GET | `/auth/me` | Get current user + privileges | Auth only |

### Tools
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| GET | `/tools` | List all tools | AI_Tool_Catalog.read |
| POST | `/tools` | Create tool | AI_Tool_Maker.write |
| GET | `/tools/:id` | Get tool with relations | AI_Tool_Catalog.read |
| PUT | `/tools/:id` | Update tool | AI_Tool_Maker.write |
| DELETE | `/tools/:id` | Delete tool | AI_Tool_Maker.write |
| POST | `/tools/:id/execute` | Execute tool (multipart/form-data) | AI_Tool_Execution.exec |

### AI Providers
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| GET | `/ai-providers` | List all (keys masked) | AI_Providers.read |
| POST | `/ai-providers` | Create provider | AI_Providers.write |
| GET | `/ai-providers/:id` | Get provider (key masked) | AI_Providers.read |
| PUT | `/ai-providers/:id` | Update provider (ignores masked key) | AI_Providers.write |
| DELETE | `/ai-providers/:id` | Delete (cannot delete default) | AI_Providers.write |
| PUT | `/ai-providers/:id/set-default` | Set as system default | AI_Providers.write |

### JSON Schemas
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| GET | `/json-schemas` | List all | Json_Schemas.read |
| POST | `/json-schemas` | Create schema | AI_Tool_Maker.write |
| GET | `/json-schemas/:id` | Get schema | Json_Schemas.read |
| PUT | `/json-schemas/:id` | Update schema | AI_Tool_Maker.write |
| DELETE | `/json-schemas/:id` | Delete schema | AI_Tool_Maker.write |

### Output Formats
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| GET | `/output-categories` | List categories with formats | Outputs_Maker.read |
| POST | `/output-categories` | Create category | Outputs_Maker.write |
| PUT | `/output-categories/:id` | Update category | Outputs_Maker.write |
| DELETE | `/output-categories/:id` | Delete category | Outputs_Maker.write |
| POST | `/output-formats` | Create format | Outputs_Maker.write |
| PUT | `/output-formats/:id` | Update format | Outputs_Maker.write |
| DELETE | `/output-formats/:id` | Delete format | Outputs_Maker.write |

### Config
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| GET | `/config` | Get all config pairs | Config.read |
| POST | `/config` | Upsert config pair | Config.write |

### Engines
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| GET | `/engines` | List all active engines | Machines.read |

### Machines
| Method | Path | Action | Privilege |
|--------|------|--------|-----------|
| GET | `/machines` | List all machines | Machines.read |
| POST | `/machines` | Create machine | Machines.write |
| GET | `/machines/:id` | Get machine with full graph | Machines.read |
| PUT | `/machines/:id` | Update machine + graph (atomic replace) | Machines.write |
| DELETE | `/machines/:id` | Delete machine (cascade) | Machines.write |

