## 10. Environment Variables

### Backend (.env)
| Variable | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| PORT | Server port | 3333 |
| DB_HOST | MySQL host | mysql-xxx.aiven.io |
| DB_PORT | MySQL port | 26213 |
| DB_NAME | Database name | inntek-ai-api-agent-manager-db |
| DB_USER | Database user | avnadmin |
| DB_PASS | Database password | *** |
| DB_SSL | Enable SSL | true |
| DB_SSL_CA | SSL CA certificate (env var for cloud) | — |
| JWT_SECRET | JWT signing secret | *** |

### Frontend (.env)
| Variable | Description | Example |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| VITE_API_URL | Backend API base URL | https://inntek-ai-api-agent-api.onrender.com/api |

### CORS Origins
- `https://inntek-ai-api-agent-client.onrender.com` (production)
- `http://localhost:5173` (development)

### Swagger Servers
- Production: `https://inntek-ai-api-agent-api.onrender.com/api`
- Development: `http://localhost:3333/api`

